00:22:59.426 --> 00:23:01.406 A:middle
And, to capture that, we can use

00:23:01.406 --> 00:23:02.466 A:middle
a top-level semantics

00:23:02.466 --> 00:23:02.836 A:middle
dictionary.

00:23:03.856 --> 00:23:05.106 A:middle
Here, I've added a semantic tag

00:23:05.106 --> 00:23:06.386 A:middle
indicating that while this pass

00:23:06.386 --> 00:23:07.866 A:middle
is relevant, silence should be

00:23:07.866 --> 00:23:08.406 A:middle
requested.

00:23:08.976 --> 00:23:11.366 A:middle
I've also indicated the duration

00:23:11.366 --> 00:23:13.036 A:middle
of the event in seconds, and

00:23:13.036 --> 00:23:14.166 A:middle
specified the event type.

00:23:14.696 --> 00:23:16.596 A:middle
You may have seen this in the

00:23:16.596 --> 00:23:18.506 A:middle
Keynote, Siri will then be able

00:23:19.046 --> 00:23:20.206 A:middle
to offer the user the ability to

00:23:20.206 --> 00:23:21.776 A:middle
quickly enable do not disturb at

00:23:21.776 --> 00:23:22.436 A:middle
the right time.

00:23:22.996 --> 00:23:24.666 A:middle
It just works.

00:23:25.006 --> 00:23:25.846 A:middle
And, it's great for things like

00:23:25.846 --> 00:23:27.576 A:middle
movie tickets, or event passes.

00:23:30.876 --> 00:23:32.316 A:middle
Now, in summary, semantic tags

00:23:32.316 --> 00:23:33.306 A:middle
are a great way to add

00:23:33.306 --> 00:23:34.596 A:middle
machine-readable content to your

00:23:34.596 --> 00:23:34.996 A:middle
passes.

00:23:36.046 --> 00:23:37.676 A:middle
And, we have over 70 supported

00:23:38.226 --> 00:23:40.056 A:middle
transit and event tags.

00:23:40.866 --> 00:23:42.576 A:middle
All these keys will be available

00:23:42.576 --> 00:23:43.706 A:middle
in our online documentation

00:23:43.706 --> 00:23:44.026 A:middle
soon.

00:23:45.146 --> 00:23:46.576 A:middle
And, one important thing to

00:23:46.576 --> 00:23:48.716 A:middle
note, relevancy information

00:23:48.716 --> 00:23:49.916 A:middle
works in combination with

00:23:49.916 --> 00:23:50.646 A:middle
semantic tags.

00:23:51.286 --> 00:23:52.176 A:middle
And so, you should add both to

00:23:52.176 --> 00:23:53.206 A:middle
your passes for the best

00:23:53.206 --> 00:23:53.806 A:middle
experience.

00:23:55.276 --> 00:23:56.746 A:middle
Now, bringing all this together,

00:23:56.846 --> 00:23:58.346 A:middle
I want to talk to you about

00:23:58.346 --> 00:23:59.666 A:middle
contactless passes.

